# Citations Bibliography

The canonical lookup table for every citation tag used in the SKIDS
protocol library. Alphabetical by tag. Markdown format.

---

## How this works

Every protocol uses bracket tags inline (e.g., `[AAP-2013-AOM]`). This
file is the lookup table that resolves each tag to its full citation.

If a tag appears in any protocol, it must have an entry here. Editorial
review fails if a protocol uses a tag that's not in this bibliography.

---

## Adding new tags

Format:

```markdown
- **[TAG]** — Full citation. Last verified: YYYY-MM-DD. [URL or DOI if available]
```

Place new entries in alphabetical order by tag.

